   "source": [
    "# 01 认识收益与风险\n",
    "\n",
    "总收益必须和回撤、波动及样本区间一起看。下面使用手工净值序列，不代表任何证券。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "from investkb.metrics import performance_summary\n",
    "\n",
    "equity = pd.Series([100, 105, 98, 112, 108, 120], dtype=float)\n",
    "performance_summary(equity)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "思考：从 100 跌到 80 是 -20%，从 80 回到 100 却需要 +25%。这就是先控制深度回撤的重要性。"
   ]
  }
